<subSubSection id="0DFA65634A64E015FF5CF891FB53F8A5" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" type="materials_examined">
<paragraph id="455F36E84A64E015FF5CF891FB53F8A5" blockId="8.[151,1437,1373,1867]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">
<emphasis id="7794EAFA4A64E015FF5CF891FE9BF8C9" bold="true" box="[199,315,1805,1831]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Remarks.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="82E04D6B4A64E015FEDEF891FDA3F8C9" authority="Meshram, 2019" authorityName="Meshram" authorityYear="2019" box="[325,515,1805,1831]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Calodia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="deergha" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="7794EAFA4A64E015FEDEF891FDA3F8C9" box="[325,515,1805,1831]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Calodia deergha</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="7794EAFA4A64E015FD96F891FDC9F8C9" bold="true" box="[525,617,1805,1831]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">
<taxonomicNameLabel id="6CA757814A64E015FD96F891FDC9F8C9" box="[525,617,1805,1831]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
resembles 
<taxonomicName id="82E04D6B4A64E015FD77F891FCC0F8C9" baseAuthorityName="Distant" box="[748,864,1805,1831]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Calodia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ostenta">
<emphasis id="7794EAFA4A64E015FD77F891FCC0F8C9" box="[748,864,1805,1831]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">C. ostenta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in general habitus but differs in having the distal process of the aedeagus 
<date id="315E10284A64E015FE3CF8ADFE63F8A5" box="[423,451,1841,1867]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">2x</date>
longer than the proximal process. They are equal in length in 
<taxonomicName id="82E04D6B4A64E015FBE0F8ADFB4CF8A5" baseAuthorityName="Distant" box="[1147,1260,1841,1867]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Calodia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ostenta">
<emphasis id="7794EAFA4A64E015FBE0F8ADFB4CF8A5" box="[1147,1260,1841,1867]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">C. ostenta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
